The first official trailer for ‘Hustlers’, which stars Cardi B, Constance Wu, Jennifer Lopez, Julia Stiles, Keke Palmer, Lizzo and Lili Reinhart has recently been released. The drama is based on the New York Magazine article “The Hustlers at Scores” by Jessica Pressler. “Hustlers follows a crew of savvy former strip club employees who band together to turn the tables on their Wall Street clients,” a press release for the film states. The release of the trailer was announced via the film’s official Instagram page with a caption that read;
“#HustlersMovie Official Trailer Hustling is a way of life. Check out the official trailer for #HustlersMovie starring @constancewu, @jlo, @missjuliastiles, @keke, @lilireinhart, @lizzobeeating, and @iamcardib – in theaters September.” https://www.instagram.com/tv/B0APFLCnR8_/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link The film which will mark Cardi’s first movie appearance was written and directed by Lorene Scafaria and will be released on September 13th, 2019. Watch the first trailer of ‘Hustlers’ via YouTube below; 